Amelia Umuhire (yavutse 1991) ni umuyobozi wa firime yu Rwanda nu Budage, producer, n'umwanditsi.

== Ubuzima ==
Umuhire yavukiye i [[Kigali]], mu Rwanda mu 1991. Afite bashiki be babiri, Anna Dushime, umunyamakuru muri Buzzfeed, na Amanda Mukasonga, bakinnye na Umuhire. Nyina Esther Mujawayo numurwanashyaka kandi uvura ihahamuka.<ref>http://ayibamagazine.com/talking-film-director-filmmaker-amelia-umuhire/</ref> Muri jenoside yo mu Rwanda 1994, ise na nyirasenge barishwe bazira ko bari abatutsi. Umuhire yahungiye mu Budage akiri баш, yiga kandi ahabwa umuhanga kUbudage сс 11. Amaze gukura, низинг нирангма n'intego mumico nyafurika na Amerika.<ref>https://www.contemporaryand.com/exhibition/amelia-umuhire-fkbp5/</ref>Umuhire yimuk i i Vienne mat matari i <ref>http://ayibamagazine.com/talking-film-director-filmmaker-amelia-umuhire/</ref>Berlin.Muri 2015, yerekanwe bwa mbere mubuyobozi hamwe nurubuga ruzwi cyane rwa ''Polyglot'' . Yakiriye igihembo cyiza cyurubuga rwubudage. Umuhire yayoboye film ngufi ''Mugabo'' muri 2016. Ifata amashusho i Kigali, igaragaramo Afro-Burayi ifata uruzinduko mu Rwanda ku nshuro ya mbere kuva jenoside yo mu 1994.<ref>https://www.contemporaryand.com/exhibition/amelia-umuhire-fkbp5/</ref>Yayoboye videwo yashinzwe ikoreshwa nkigikorwa cyo kuzenguruka isabukuru yimyaka ''[[Miseducation y'umusozi wa Lauryn|20 ya Miseducation ya Lauryn Hill]]''<ref>https://www.e-flux.com/video/331962/amelia-umuhire-nbsp-polyglot-ep-2-le-mal-du-pays-nbsp-homesickness/</ref>Muri 2018, Umuhire yayoboye podcast yubuzima bwa se.Yiswe ''Vaterland'', yatowe muri Prix Europa. Yayoboye amashusho ya ''King Who'', yafatiwe amashusho kwa nyirasenge, muri 2019. <ref>https://mcachicago.org/Publications/Blog/2018/Speaking-From-The-Void-A-Conversation-With-Filmmaker-Amelia-Umuhire</ref>Umuhire yahawe igihembo cya [[Igihembo cya Villa Romana|Villa Romana]] muri 2020<ref>https://www.contemporaryand.com/magazines/amelia-umuhire-unpacking-hidden-rwandese-stories/</ref>Yakoze amajwi yubushakashatsi hamwe namashusho ya ''Kana'' kubyerekeranye nubuzima kuri Mars muri 2020<ref>http://www.daily-lazy.com/2020/09/amelia-umuhire-at-gemeinde-koln-cologne.html</ref>

bikorwa bye byerekanwe mu birori byinshi bya firime, harimo MOCA Los Angeles, MCA Chicago, Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Tribeca, Iserukiramuco rya Filime ry’Abanyamerika muri Smithsonian, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filimi Rotterdam.<ref>https://www.contemporaryand.com/exhibition/amelia-umuhire-fkbp5/</ref>

